            - *RECOVER Energize*: Structured pacing for PEM
                ($n=600$); completing December 2025
            - *LDN trial*: Low-dose naltrexone for fatigue in
                ages 6–25; enrolment estimated summer 2026
            - *GLP-1 agonist trial*: Targeting immune
                dysregulation; enrolment estimated late summer 2026
        
